g.title: j4099881520
g.text: Hello my darling.

g.title: j2963047803->j4099881520
g.text: true

g.title: j3004613107
g.text: Hello, mysterious and oddly compelling stranger from another time.

g.title: j2963047803->j3004613107
g.text: false

g.title: j3080734783
g.text: Did you sleep better last night?

g.title: j957073842
g.text: Did you have another nightmare?

g.title: j3208567288
g.text: I haven’t had the Arthur dream once since I told you about Granny Callie. I think you exorcized that demon.

g.title: j2437281582
g.text: Check boolean EleanorDating

g.title: j229918797
g.text: But since we’ve been together, something else has been happening. It’s a bit awkward actually. I’ve been meaning to talk to you about it, but there hasn’t been a good time.

g.title: j2437281582->j229918797
g.text: true

g.title: j3807406937
g.text: But that's not to say there haven't been OTHER dreams. Rather disturbing ones.

g.title: j2437281582->j3807406937
g.text: false

g.title: j2987353514
g.text: You’re dreaming about me?

g.title: j1123028117
g.text: You’re dreaming about us?

g.title: j915390759
g.text: Awkward? This doesn’t sound good.

g.title: j644156132
g.text: I don't think you disturb easily.

g.title: j3560810351
g.text: Falling down an endless flight of stairs?

g.title: j3564133260
g.text: Could be important. With your ability, a dream might not be just a dream.

g.title: j4040373596
g.text: That wouldn't be awkward. This is.

g.title: j1012584566
g.text: Gods, I wish. Nothing so pleasant, I'm afraid.

g.title: j2956550727
g.text: Don’t worry. It’s not bad as such. I’m not frightened. It’s just...

g.title: j3227412225
g.text: I don't, which is why this is so troubling.

g.title: j3983565151
g.text: No, not that one. Funny that everyone seems to have had it, though.

g.title: j2198805794
g.text: That's exactly what I'm afraid of.

g.title: j1343802935
g.text: (Okay, Eleanor, deep breath, you can do this)

g.title: j1656980580
g.text: (Okay, Eleanor, deep breath, you can do this)

g.title: j4252287713
g.text: I think the Techrot’s jealous.

g.title: j1279936511
g.text: I think the Techrot’s jealous.

g.title: j3242779728
g.text: You have got to be joking.

g.title: j1285571050
g.text: Jealous?

g.title: j2781228363
g.text: You have got to be joking.

g.title: j3618468579
g.text: Jealous?

g.title: j1909811206
g.text: Oh, how I wish I were.

g.title: j3779179828
g.text: Jealous of you for taking me away, yes.

g.title: j10126738
g.text: Oh, how I wish I were.

g.title: j44347089
g.text: Jealous of our friendship, yes.

g.title: j2012486102
g.text: On some profoundly messed up level, it thinks of me as its property. I was meant to be its breeding prospect. The Legacytes see me as a rival queen, you know.

g.title: j3055175055
g.text: On some profoundly messed up level, it thinks of me as its property. I was meant to be its breeding prospect. The Legacytes see me as a rival queen, you know.

g.title: j3834578939
g.text: That’s not how Warframes work. The Infestation in them is tamed, it’s dormant. Except for Nidus, I guess, but he’s a law unto himself.

g.title: j1430530206
g.text: So the Techrot thinks I stole you from it, and now it wants you back?

g.title: j838764335
g.text: That’s not how Warframes work. The Infestation in them is tamed, it’s dormant. Except for Nidus, I guess, but he’s a law unto himself.

g.title: j3193644022
g.text: So the Techrot thinks I'm keeping you from going back to it?

g.title: j3737452589
g.text: Well, maybe if I were a full Warframe, the Techrot wouldn't see me this way. As it is, my cells are still fizzling, and it sees me as its own.

g.title: j1555884561
g.text: Isn’t it bizarre? The jilted ex!

g.title: j1677744157
g.text: Well, maybe if I were a full Warframe, the Techrot wouldn't see me this way. As it is, my cells are still fizzling, and it sees me as its own.

g.title: j1268571310
g.text: Yes. It wants me back in its gang.

g.title: j1558753592
g.text: Where I come from, you’d have to go and have a fight with it round the back of the local supermarket. I’m not sure how it works in your time.

g.title: j3294040798
g.text: This is your REAL family, it whispers. Become part of us again, severed sister. Be accepted.

g.title: j2178102419
g.text: Wait, back up a bit. How do you know that’s what the Techrot is feeling?

g.title: j3666367511
g.text: Oh Gods, this is the awkward bit.

g.title: j318348419
g.text: The dreams I mentioned before? I'm certain the Techrot's sending them.

g.title: j1821383998
g.text: Whatever that stuff has that passes for a mind, it’s always been able to connect with mine. The thoughts it sends are always so crude and weak I can easily fend them off.

g.title: j4057890675
g.text: Most of the time it just feels like this frantic scratching at the back of my skull, like when you’re in the loo and there’s a cat trying to get the door open.

g.title: j855594132
g.text: But when you’re asleep it’s a different story, right?

g.title: j3707214731
g.text: I think I can see where this is going.

g.title: j2595515866
g.text: Right. My defenses are down, and it can reach me.

g.title: j95707898
g.text: It’s been hitting me on the most primordial level, if you know what I mean. It wants me back. It promises it can make me feel ecstasy I’ve never known.

g.title: j265516035
g.text: It will seed my flesh with the dripping cysts of new life. Because it thinks that’s what I want, you see.

g.title: j2297967962
g.text: Check boolean EleanorDating

g.title: j2372127785
g.text: Okay, I guess that’s it for us. How can I compete with that?

g.title: j2297967962->j2372127785
g.text: true

g.title: j547940779
g.text: I will *burn it all* before I let it take you.

g.title: j2297967962->j547940779
g.text: true

g.title: j1439748047
g.text: I'm never going to let it take you, Eleanor. You're my friend.

g.title: j2297967962->j1439748047
g.text: false

g.title: j259049845
g.text: You're like family to me. I won't let it have you.

g.title: j2297967962->j259049845
g.text: false

g.title: j3281619093
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j1173596322
g.text: Now that's the kind of talk that gets a Drifter absolutely covered with kisses.

g.title: j4211836569
g.text: I know. I think it knows, too, which is why it's so angry. It can't compete.

g.title: j1973764472
g.text: I'll sleep easier knowing you have my back.

g.title: j1198239196
g.text: It’s okay, my sweet. I’m not about to leave you for a suppurating mass of tubercular flesh with lumps of orphaned technology floating in it.

g.title: j3735471117
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j166815700
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j4242443010
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j2292021818
g.text: Just… if you see me looking especially dark-eyed and gaunt on any particular morning when we wake up together, please bring me a nice strong coffee and don’t press me for details?

g.title: j2953760057
g.text: Fancy giving the Techrot something to be REALLY jealous of?

g.title: j3947400502
g.text: We'll face it together, then. Side by side. Always.

g.title: j465089057
g.text: We're family. Blood and found. Unbreakable.

g.title: j1810700159
g.text: I can do that.

g.title: j98825980
g.text: ...Noted.
